        "setup": "Go to [Register For An App Key](https://api.stackexchange.com/) or [Stack Apps app registration](https://stackapps.com/apps/oauth/register) and create an application. This gives you the `client_id` used by OAuth flows and lets you enable OAuth for your app. In the June 2025 Stack Apps dashboard you can also name and rotate multiple API keys and client secrets for the same app.",
