        "label": "Stack Exchange API key",
        "generateUrl": "https://stackapps.com/apps/oauth/register",
        "setup": "In your Stack Apps application, click **Generate API Key**. Store the value securely because Stack Apps will not show it again. Use it for public API access and to increase throttle quota. API keys are also required when using OAuth-authenticated requests.",
